    <title>A bill to remove the authority of the Secretary of Energy to amend or issue new energy efficiency standards for ceiling fans.</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <updateDate>2015-04-22T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
